item.description:
@_Rich wrote:

[code] case 237:
int castOnSlot = inStream.readSignedWord();
int castOnItem = inStream.readSignedWordA();
int castSpell = inStream.readSignedWordA();
int alchvaluez = (int) Math.floor(GetItemShopValue(castOnItem, 0, castOnSlot));

	if (!playerHasItem(castOnItem))
		return;
	if (castSpell == 1178) {
		if (playerLevel[6] > 54) {
			if (playerHasItemAmount(561, 1) && System.currentTimeMillis() - ActionDelay > 2500) {
				if (playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == 3053 || playerHasItemAmount(554, 5)) {
					deleteItem(castOnItem, castOnSlot, 1);
					addItem(995, alchvaluez);
					addSkillXP(1750, 6);
					setSidebarMage();
					anim(713);
					gfx(113);
					delete(561, 1);
					if (playerHasItemAmount(554, 5) && playerEquipment[playerWeapon] != 3053) {
						delete(554, 5);
					}
					ActionDelay = System.currentTimeMillis();
				} else {
					sendMsg("You do not have enough runes to cast this spell.");
				}
			}
		} else {
			sendMsg("You need at least 55 Magic to cast High Level Alchemy");
		}
	}

					alchvaluez = (alchvaluez / 5);
					deleteItem(castOnItem, castOnSlot, 1);
					addItem(995, alchvaluez);
					addSkillXP(600, 6);
					setSidebarMage();
					anim(712);
					gfx(112);
					delete(561, 1);
					if (playerHasItemAmount(554, 3) && playerEquipment[playerWeapon] != 3053) {
						delete(554, 3);
					}
					ActionDelay = System.currentTimeMillis();
				} else {
					sendMsg("You do not have enough runes to cast this spell.");
				}
			}
		} else {
			sendMsg("You need at least 15 Magic to cast Low Level Alchemy");
		}
	}
	break;[/code]
